modules.description: This module parses and handles multipart/form-data streams using both streaming and in-memory approaches. It provides `stream` to process multipart data incrementally, returning a stream of parts with user-defined identification, and `save_part` to write individual parts to files. The non-streaming functions `of_stream_to_list` and `of_stream_to_tree` collect all parts into memory, suitable for small form submissions where direct access to all data is needed.
